  "detailed_description": "<h1>TRY MY OTHER GAME:</h1><p></p><br><h1>OTHER AWESOME DECKBUILDERS</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><i>Malice & Greed</i> is a roguelike turn-based RPG inspired by <i>Shin Megami Tensei & Persona</i>, combined with elements of deckbuilders like <i>Slay the Spire</i>. Force <strong>every enemy & boss </strong>to join your team, swapping allies in & out during combat as you please!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/2afb4141a86098be7354a50484d3c95e.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After battle, the final defeated enemy <i><strong>joins you</strong></i>! Will you risk saving the strongest for last?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/335dbaf8aeb210167ac09d9c6e896e69.poster.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/335dbaf8aeb210167ac09d9c6e896e69.webm?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/335dbaf8aeb210167ac09d9c6e896e69.mp4?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/bb8b74e847235332049c2ee9b89e5119.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Butcher</i></strong> enemies to steal their skills for yourself, and create the ultimate build!<br></li><li><strong><i>Fuse</i></strong> enemies together to customize them to your liking!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/9e643a0236b481fc6c0afb84a4df26d9.poster.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/9e643a0236b481fc6c0afb84a4df26d9.webm?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/9e643a0236b481fc6c0afb84a4df26d9.mp4?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Mix & match skills of <strong>4 Colors</strong> to explore new playstyles each run. You gain power each turn letting you use stronger skills as the fight goes on - but so does the enemy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/7d059c499f6860b5a5e9bf24a233989b.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=492 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/21219b10f7dca03b4588f16236497f2b.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br></li><li>Sell unwanted allies to the <strong><i>Shady Smuggler</i></strong> to get powerful relics and upgrades!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/319d22caefb49026e3c45aadceac93c1.poster.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/319d22caefb49026e3c45aadceac93c1.webm?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/319d22caefb49026e3c45aadceac93c1.mp4?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/689fc7891113c428419b1320520de887.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br></li><li>Build <strong><i>broken combos</i></strong> by abusing the synergies of skills & systems!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/7f15d814380cac2109bd0c6e0fbb26e0.poster.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/7f15d814380cac2109bd0c6e0fbb26e0.webm?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/7f15d814380cac2109bd0c6e0fbb26e0.mp4?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/637993c7e70769c0694ee04152e07d18.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Sacrifice allies</strong> to defy death using <strong><i>Demonform</i></strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/af059ee8b99f2a6fa235006c88de380b.poster.avif?t=1710393505\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/af059ee8b99f2a6fa235006c88de380b.webm?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/af059ee8b99f2a6fa235006c88de380b.mp4?t=1710393505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Something New Every Run!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use over 500 skills and 80 relics that make each run unique.<br></li><li> Trade your \"Allies\" - Your party members are your currency.<br></li><li> Unlock & Customize 3 powerful Demonic transformations.<br></li><li> Force over 20 bosses and 70 enemies to join your team - Each with 5 different versions to choose from.<br></li><li> Spend your resources between runs to unlock new features & upgrades.</li></ul>",
